location.city_name: Terrace Theater, Long Beach Performing Arts Center

social_posts.post_text: @jokoy sold out all 4 shows in Long Beach Terrace Theater this week!!! This is a very special place to Joe, the great Richard Pryor rocked this stage and filmed one of the most famous comedy specials here! Tonight we have one more, excited for another special night!

When JoKoy says "Hey Joey meet my good friend @apollonia_kotero " I was so shy because I just watched Purple Rain for the 25th time!  Such a pleasure meeting her, so sweet and she blessed us with kind words and the best energy 🙌🏾❤️🙌🏾 So nice meeting you!! 💜

I would like to let the world know that today is my Mommy's Birthday!!!!!! Thank you Mom for everything you have done for me and the family. You have the biggest kindest heart and you always cook amazing dishes with love!! Happy Birthday Mom I love you so much!!!!!

Love Lil Joey
When that extra Expresso shot hit different.

Help me wish a big Happy Birthday to this young lady with the biggest heart @bonjoey519 !! Thank you Bonnie for all your support and all you do for us and the fur kids! We the same age now, we going to Denny's and to the 🕺 Disco!! Hahaha jk love you beautiful !!! Happppyyy Birthdayyy!

@bonjoey519 and I had a wonderful time with The Luna Familia celebrating our beautiful big hearted Goddaughter @miagraceluna Quinceanera !!! Thank you @teamluna2 & @lunafam17 for having us!! We had a blast, love you guys!!

My goddaughter @miagraceluna showing me a few moves after I ate hella cake at her Quinceanera. My legs have not moved like that since 1986 lol. 

Video by her mom @teamluna2 who was cheering for my feet to keep moving! Lol
Good Morning! 🇨🇦

An amazing weekend in @jokoy hometown Tacoma where he sold out and KILLED IT  at The Tacoma Dome with over 20,000 people! The mayor gave him the 🔑 Key to the city and announced Dec 11 the official "Jokoy Day"

Hearing the roaring laughter gave me the chills, Jokoy, @jabbawockeez and @djturbulence destroyed it!!! Just when everyone thought the show was over Joe brings out @macklemore and he shut it down!! 

My favorite part  is when he brought his son @josephhherbert , his sister Gemma @jokoy_fanpage and his Dad on stage at the end!! Love it !!

Excited for next years World Tour Merry Xmas everyone ! ❤️
